<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>感觉 on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/tags/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89/</link><description>Recent content in 感觉 on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:13:44 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/tags/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>感觉器官的功能</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 20:18:49 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</guid><description>&lt;p>感觉（sensation）是客观物质世界在脑的主观反映，是机体赖以生存的重要功能活动之一。感觉的产生是感受器或感觉器官、神经传导通路和感觉中枢三部分共同活动的结果。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>最简单的感受器就是游离的传入神经末梢，而有些在结构和功能上都高度分化的感受细胞连同它们的附属结构则一道构成了感觉器官，主要有哏、耳、鼻、舌及皮肤等。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>躯体和内脏感觉</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E8%BA%AF%E4%BD%93%E5%92%8C%E5%86%85%E8%84%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 20:37:42 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E8%BA%AF%E4%BD%93%E5%92%8C%E5%86%85%E8%84%8F%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89/</guid><description>躯体感觉 内脏感觉 痛觉 感觉器官的功能#感受器的一般生理特性痛觉（pain）是一种与组织损伤有关的感觉、情感、认知和社会维度的痛苦体验。 痛觉感受</description></item><item><title>视觉</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:13:25 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%89/</guid><description>&lt;p>人眼的适宜刺激是波长 380&amp;ndash;760 nm 的电磁波，即可见光。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>听觉</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E5%90%AC%E8%A7%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:13:33 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E5%90%AC%E8%A7%89/</guid><description>&lt;p>人耳能够感受的声波频率范围是 20&amp;ndash;20000Hz，耳&lt;mark>最敏感的声波频率范围为 1000&amp;ndash;3000Hz&lt;/mark>，人的语言频率主要分布在 300&amp;ndash;3000Hz 范围内。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>平衡感觉</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 21:13:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E6%84%9F%E8%A7%89/</guid><description>&lt;p>内耳的前庭器官由半规管、椭圆囊和球囊组成，其主要功能是感受机体姿势和运动状态（运动觉）以及头部在空间的位置（位置觉），这些感觉合称为平衡感觉。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>